Text: Some think aliens are demonic in nature, spiritual beings. So I can see why they would make the connection between aliens and human sacrifices and cults. Personally I have no opinion on aliens, I am not convinced they are beings from another world or if they are real at all. But I do find it interesting. So i will watch this, thanks for uploading it.
